OOC: There are Tripreds about 6 km away from your base! Thank you for 
noticing!

BIC: The Hellgate landed in Northern Italia. Daemos came out of the 
ship and took a small crate along with him. The terrain was grassy and 
small hills protruded from the ground.

Daemos: I will go in bot mode. I can not fly in beast mode...

He spread his four wings and lifted from the ground. He picked some 
speed and flew towards the Etna. He had taken the crate and held it 
tightly. Inside were the seeds of war...
